==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Impartment
<hw>Im*part"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
imparting, or that which is imparted, communicated, or disclosed.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It beckons you to go away with it,⟦br⟧
As if it some <qex>impartment</qex> did desire⟦br⟧
To you alone.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Impassable</ent>⟦br⟧
